title: Roast battle UK S01 SEASON 01
description:
Roast Battle was a British stand-up roast comedy show that was broadcast on Comedy Central (UK & Ireland) and its first series had a total of six episodes which aired consecutive episodes from January 15, 2018 until January 19, 2018.[1] The show featured Jimmy Carr as the host and presenter and also featured famous stand-up comedians facing each other in roast battles, similar to that of the American television show created by Comedy Central, Comedy Central Roasts and Jeff Ross Presents: Roast Battle.

Roast Battle made headlines as it became Comedy Central's highest-rated UK commission in history
